 * Purpose

 Pandoc is an useful tool to convert markdown to html/pdf/epub. It can do more things than this.

 * Install

 ```
 yum install pandoc
 yum install texlive  #Converting to pdf needs this tool
 ```

 * Usage

 Convert to html:
 ```
 pandoc test1.md -f markdown -t html -s -o test1.html
 ```
`-s`: standalone

 Convert to pdf:
 ```
 pandoc test1.md -s -o test1.pdf
 ```

 * Reference

 - http://pandoc.org/getting-started.html

